      <title>摩根士丹利的威尔逊认为近期利润大幅下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-11/morgan-stanley-s-wilson-sees-big-drop-in-near-term-profit-views</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根士丹利 (Morgan Stanley) 的迈克尔·威尔逊 (Michael Wilson) 表示，由于利润率面临压力，美国公司盈利可能会在 2024 年第四季度出现疲软，然后出现反弹。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-11/morgan-stanley-s-wilson-sees-big-drop-in-near-term-profit-views</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 Dec 2023 09:45:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>消息人士称，日本央行认为没有必要在 12 月结束负利率</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-11/boj-is-said-to-see-little-need-to-end-negative-rate-in-december</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，日本央行官员认为本月没有必要急于废除全球最后一次负利率，因为他们尚未看到足够的证据表明工资增长将支持可持续通胀。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-11/boj-is-said-to-see-little-need-to-end-negative-rate-in-december</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 Dec 2023 07:40:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国的实际借贷成本飙升至2016年以来的最高水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-11/china-s-surging-real-borrowing-costs-to-drag-on-growth-into-2024</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于通货紧缩压力挥之不去，预计2024年中国的实际借贷成本将保持在高位，这对世界第二大经济体的增长构成又一个威胁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-11/china-s-surging-real-borrowing-costs-to-drag-on-growth-into-2024</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 Dec 2023 06:35:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>埃塞俄比亚债券息票小姐将使其成为非洲最新的违约者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-11/ethiopia-is-about-to-become-africa-s-next-debt-defaulter</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃塞俄比亚似乎将无法支付周一晚些时候到期的 2024 年 12 月美元债券的利息，成为最新一个出现债务违约的新兴市场主权国家。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-11/ethiopia-is-about-to-become-africa-s-next-debt-defaulter</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 Dec 2023 03:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
